        "action": "provide free water for everyone on the street of UK in this extreme hot weather",
        "additional_details": "The condition is extremely hot and people can get dehydrated and homeless people are at higher risk. Water must be provided by the local government in form of a water fountain or local shops providing them by local council finding them. This is a government\u2019s duty to keep their people safe.",
        "background": "I think water must be free in this hot weather for everyone specially homeless people living on the street. The government must provide funding to local councils to facilitate the supply of free water in the street on UK. The local government must help local shops to provide water to everyone.",
